# Analytics endpoint — the landing site's Next.js API route that records opt-in,
# anonymous usage events. Copy this file to `.env` and set the deployed URL.
#
# Example: https://your-domain.com/api/events
#
# If left unset, analytics are a silent no-op — the extension works exactly as
# before. Analytics also never fire unless the user opts in via Settings.

VITE_ANALYTICS_ENDPOINT=
